
###############################################################################
###################### How to run this project ################################
###############################################################################


To execute this project, follow the few coming steps:

1. This project needs a MySql database (of users and their roles). To create it, 
activate the main method of the class 'UserManager.java' 
inside the package 'technou.com.utilities' by uncommenting it.

2. Run this class as 'Java Application'.

3. After successfully creating the database (named 'usersmanagement') with some 
users and their roles, disable again this main method. you will not need it later.

4. Run now the whole project as 'Spring Boot App'.

5. Open in a browser the Url 'http://localhost:8080/index' to start the web-app.
